# Add Memory tests for migration, claim exclusivity, stale reclaim, and session-scoped cleanup

## Requirements

- Add focused tests for queue schema migration and low-level queue API behavior.
- Cover exclusivity and stale-claim recovery, not just happy-path enqueue/dequeue.
- Verify session-scoped cleanup behavior so future reset semantics are grounded in tests.

## Acceptance Criteria

- Tests prove migration creates the new queue table and does not lose existing data.
- Tests cover enqueue, exclusive claim semantics, stale-claim reclaim, and per-session clear behavior.
- Tests fail if queue operations regress FIFO-oriented ordering assumptions or cleanup boundaries.
